Logo Construction 
Clarity Structure Reliable 
The Glaido logo is a refined mark that unites communication and technology into a single, memorable shape. Formed as a rounded letter “G” that also functions as a chat bubble, the symbol reflects the core of the Glaido platform, clear, intuitive, and continuous interaction.   
Its open structure suggests flow and accessibility, while the precise geometry introduces a modern, tech-forward character. This balance of softness and structure positions Glaido as both approachable and reliable.   
The result is a visual identity that embodies clarity, motion, and smart communication, reinforcing Glaido’s mission to make information easier to share, understand, and act upon. 
